# ============================================================================
# VERIFICATION NOTES
# ============================================================================
# To verify this works correctly:
# 
# 1. Place article_data.csv in data/ directory
# 2. Run: git status
# 3. You should NOT see data/article_data.csv listed
# 4. You SHOULD see data/README.md listed (if new)
#
# If article_data.csv appears in git status:
# - Check that data/*.csv is in this file (it is)
# - Check that *.csv is in this file (it is)
# - Run: git check-ignore -v data/article_data.csv
#   This will show which rule is excluding it
